properties.name: Sam's Sushi
properties.description: Posted by Jenniferhaywood 5506 22nd Avenue Northwest, Seattle, WA, 98107My favorite Seattle restaurant. The sushi is delicious, as is the tempura (especially the shrimp), and they have an amazing dish called the Crunchy Roll which is so scrumptious I don\'t mind that it always falls apart on me. The tea there is also amazing! And free! I love to go in on a cold day, sit down, and be given a cup of tea to warm my hands and face--it smells wonderful! Sam\'s also is very reasonable, and the waitresses are very efficient and polite. Love it!
